<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Application Status - E-schools</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Prompt:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');
        body {
            font-family: 'Prompt', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: rgb(30 64 175);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 0 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .email-header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .email-body p {
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: rgb(30 64 175);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .email-footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        a {
            color: #325fe0;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Application Status - E-schools</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
        <p>Dear {{ institution.title }} Team,</p>
        <p>Thank you for your interest in joining <strong>E-schools</strong>â€”the platform dedicated to electronic and remote learning. We appreciate the time and effort you put into your application.</p>
        <p>Unfortunately, after careful review, we regret to inform you that your application has not been approved at this time.</p>
        <p>The primary reason(s) for this decision:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>{{ reason }}</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We encourage you to review the feedback and consider reapplying in the future if the situation changes.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need further clarification, please do not hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:support@eschools.com">support@eschools.com</a>.</p>
        <p>Thank you once again for considering E-schools.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>The E-schools Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
        <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} E-schools. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>You are receiving this email because you applied to join our platform.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
